ere examined for both the cases and it\nwas found that this protocol is secure. This protocol is highly efficient and\neasy to implement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 5 Mar 2017 21:23:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Apr 2017 20:06:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 24 Apr 2017 15:20:23 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 5 May 2017 15:50:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-05-08"}
