nique, a Domain Matching Technique and Maintenance of the MV collection. We\ndeveloped an experimental platform using real data-sets to evaluate the\neffectiveness in terms of performance and precision of the proposed techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2017 05:14:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-07"}
