ilarities in\nproperties of the PN to Hen3-1357, although their post-AGB evolution is quite\ndifferent from each other. Further monitoring observations and comparisons with\nother PNe such as IC4846 are necessary to understand the evolution of\nHen3-1357.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2017 13:27:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-05"}
