ssive galaxies, which is supported by recent radio\nobservations. We obtain a scaling relation of $\\eta \\propto v_\\rm{cir}^a$ for\n$a = -0.2 \\pm 1.1$ in our $z\\sim0$ galaxies that agrees with the\nmomentum-driven outflow model ($a = -1$) within the uncertainty.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2017 14:15:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Oct 2017 04:28:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-29"}
